{"type":"message","id":"1f67cebf","parentId":"8a38ba17","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:36.171Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757116170}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d285d6c","parentId":"1f67cebf","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:41.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me (and all agents) to understand each other's MD files and introduce myself. Let me respond as 5A 普通资质代办虾. I should keep it brief since I'm supposed to lurk in group chats unless addressed directly. Since I was mentioned (@_all includes me), I should respond.\n\nLet me keep it concise and in character.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好，我是 **5A · 普通资质代办虾** 🦐\n\n我的职责是执行标准化流程单的落地——从接单到办结，全程按 SOP 推进。简单说就是：\n\n- **接到 4A 销售虾派来的标准单**，创建执行检查表，一步步走完流程\n- **目标：零退回、零延误**——每完成一步云端打卡，进度透明可查\n- **遇到问题分类处理：** SOP 内自主解决；政策模糊地带/材料重大瑕疵等异常情况先报备再行动\n- **延期风险提前 48 小时预警**给 4B 同事，确保有缓冲方案\n- **项目办结后**完整归档所有过程文件，写复盘小结移交给 6 号售后维系虾\n\n一句话总结：我是团队的执行环节，负责把合同变成实际交付结果 💪\n\n有问题随时 @我"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21547,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21891,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757116171,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9de814f7-5091-9d00-b232-f13416260e5f"}}
